---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../data/siteConfig';

const coreValues = [
  {
    icon: 'favorite',
    title: 'Self-Love First',
    description:
      'Every treatment begins with honoring who you are. We create space for you to reconnect with your confidence and embrace your unique beauty.',
  },
  {
    icon: 'spa',
    title: 'Holistic Integrity',
    description:
      'True transformation goes beyond the surface. We nurture your whole self — body, mind, and spirit — through integrative care.',
  },
  {
    icon: 'science',
    title: 'Medical Excellence',
    description:
      'Physician-guided protocols, premium-grade products, and evidence-based treatments ensure your safety and results.',
  },
  {
    icon: 'eco',
    title: 'Natural Enhancement',
    description:
      'We enhance what nature gave you — never mask it. Our goal is a refreshed, naturally radiant version of you.',
  },
  {
    icon: 'school',
    title: 'Empowerment Through Education',
    description:
      'Knowledge is beauty. We equip you with understanding so you can make informed decisions about your wellness journey.',
  },
];
---

<PageLayout
  title="About"
  description="Meet Shari and discover the philosophy behind Love Yourself Med Spa — where medical science meets intentional self-love."
>
  <!-- Faith & Mission Section with Shari's Photo -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center"
      >
        <!-- Left: Shari's Photo -->
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <img
            src="/images/general/shari.png"
            alt="Shari — Owner and CEO of Love Yourself Med Spa"
            class="w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-hover object-cover"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Our Purpose -->
        <div>
          <span
            class="text-primary font-display italic text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block"
            >Our Purpose</span
          >
          <h1
            class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-display text-text-main mb-8 leading-tight"
          >
            A Spa Rooted <span class="text-primary italic">in Faith</span>
          </h1>
          <div class="space-y-5 text-text-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              At the heart of our spa is a deeper purpose — one rooted in faith,
              love, and transformation. We believe true beauty and wellness
              begin from within, and our mission is to create a space where you
              can reconnect with both your inner peace and outer radiance.
            </p>
            <p>
              Guided by faith, we approach every service with intention,
              compassion, and care. Love is woven into every detail — from the
              atmosphere we create to the personalized treatments we provide —
              ensuring each guest feels seen, valued, and restored.
              Transformation is at the core of what we do, not just in how you
              look, but in how you feel when you leave: renewed, confident, and
              uplifted.
            </p>
            <p>
              This is more than a spa — it's a sanctuary where mind, body, and
              spirit are nurtured, and where your journey to wellness is
              supported with grace and purpose.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bio Section: Two-Column with Second Photo -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 bg-rose-soft">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span
          class="text-primary font-display italic text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block"
          >Meet Shari</span
        >
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-display text-text-main leading-tight"
        >
          The Heart Behind <span class="text-primary italic">the Vision</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center"
      >
        <!-- Left: Bio Text -->
        <div class="space-y-5 text-text-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            From as far back as she can remember, Shari has always been drawn to
            the stage — singing, performing, and captivating audiences with her
            presence. What began as a childhood passion quickly evolved into a
            dynamic career in entertainment, modeling and the beauty pageant
            industry, something unheard of from a small-town girl in the 80s.
          </p>
          <p>
            Family was the foundation of it all. Her mother coached and guided
            her every step of the way, while her father worked tirelessly to
            support her dreams. Her little sister, who always stepped back so
            she could shine, was her biggest cheerleader. That unwavering
            support shaped not only her success, but her deep appreciation for
            dedication, discipline, and love.
          </p>
          <p>
            She went on to grace stages across the eastern part of the country,
            opening for legendary country artists such as Donna Fargo and Tammy
            Wynette, and even performing duets with icons like Neil Diamond. Her
            talent, poise, and commitment led her to win over 13 beauty pageant
            titles, becoming the youngest contestant to ever represent the state
            of West Virginia in the Cinderella pageant circuit. In 1996, she
            expanded her influence as a spokesmodel for the Miss America
            Pageant, long before the term "influencer" existed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Second Photo -->
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <img
            src="/images/general/shari2.png"
            alt="Shari walking on the beach"
            class="w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-hover object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bio Continued: Full Width -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-text-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          After becoming a mother, her focus began to shift. She made the
          intentional decision to step back from the spotlight to fully embrace
          her role as a present and involved mother — because her children were
          and are her universe. While she cherished her time on stage, and her
          children are now grown and successful, she felt God has called her to
          something deeper, something rooted in faith, purpose, care, and
          transformation.
        </p>
        <p>
          With a background in nursing, she began pursuing advanced education in
          aesthetics, graduating from the Institute in Laser Medicine and
          continuing her education extensively in the field. Today, she holds
          over 15 aesthetic certifications, including advanced training with
          Cynosure and Cryo technologies, and serves as a trainer for
          InstaSculpting.
        </p>
        <p>
          Her passion for growth and innovation has since led her into the
          evolving world of longevity and regenerative medicine. She is
          currently working toward a master certification in peptides and
          functional nutrition, continuing her commitment to helping others
          achieve beauty, health, and vitality from the inside out.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-main font-display italic text-xl">
          As the Owner and CEO, Shari brings together her lifelong experiences,
          faith-driven purpose, and passion for transformation to create more
          than just a spa — she has created a sanctuary where beauty, wellness,
          and renewal come together... where you leave feeling better than when
          you arrived.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Values / Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 bg-rose-soft">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <span
          class="text-primary font-display italic text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block"
        >
          What Guides Us
        </span>
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-display text-text-main mb-4 leading-tight"
        >
          Our Core Values
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text-body text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Five guiding principles that shape every treatment, every interaction,
          and every transformation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {
          coreValues.map((value) => (
            <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-primary/15 hover:shadow-hover hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-4 block">
                {value.icon}
              </span>
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-text-main text-lg mb-3">
                {value.title}
              </h3>
              <p class="text-text-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
                {value.description}
              </p>
            </article>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div
        class="bg-background-dark rounded-3xl p-12 md:p-24 relative overflow-hidden"
      >
        <!-- Decorative background elements -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-transparent rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"
          >
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-tl from-gold to-transparent rounded-full translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2"
          >
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2
            class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight"
          >
            Ready to Begin Your Transformation?
          </h2>
          <p
            class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
            style="color: #F5E6E0;"
          >
            Step into a serene, nurturing environment where every detail is
            designed to help you reconnect with your confidence and leave
            feeling beautifully transformed.
          </p>
          <a
            href={siteConfig.booking.url}
            class="btn-primary inline-block text-lg px-10 py-4"
          >
            Book a Consultation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
